The temporary traffic changes are as follows:

  • If congestion is observed on Irvine Street the Western Entry detour will be implemented,Â traffic at Irvine Street will be diverted to the University Western Access route via Murphys Avenue and Robsons Road during peak periods.Â Â 
  • Motorists accessing the M1 northbound ramp (towards Sydney) at Northfields Avenue during peak periods will be diverted via Murphys Avenue and Robsons Road.Â Â 

Bus access from University Avenue into Irvine Street will not be affected during diversions and outside peak periods traffic will continue to access the University via Irvine Street and Northfields Avenue.
